name: Outlets at Anthem
info: Outlets at Anthem is located in Phoenix, Arizona has 37 stores. It is one of the most popular outlet mall in Arizona beacuse of their Decoration during the hoilday season.

name: Phoenix General Store
info: The Phoenix General Store has clothing, gifts, and home products that are inspired by the life in a desert city.It is very popular for it's clothes beacuse it has won the Best Clothing Store award 2 years in a row.

name: Tempe Marketplace
address: 2000 E Rio Salado Pkwy, Tempe, AZ 85281
info: Tempe Marketplace has over 100 shops and restaurants to choose from and has many events. It is the best place for out-of-town visitors beacuse of it's of vibrant outdoor environment, cozy fireplaces, unique water features and lsuh landscape.

name: Cameron Trading Post
info: Cameron Trading Post has stores, restaurants and hotels. Their shop have Native Amercian jewelry, pottery, basketry and more.

name: Pinspiration Peoria
address: 6520 W Happy Valley Rd Suite B-103, Glendale, AZ 85310
info: Pinspiration Peoria is a DIY Craft Studio where people can work on projects together.It is one of the best craft studio in Arizona. You can make anything from cups to decorations for a party.

name: Tlaquepaque Arts & Shopping Village
info: Tlaquepaque Arts & Shopping Village is one of the best and distinctive places to shop in Sedona. All of the their shops have authenticate fashion design from a traditional mexican village.

name: Biltmore Fashion Park
info: Biltmore Fashion Park is a luxury shopping center in the Biltmore District. It has alot of luxury stores from around the world.

name: Mountain Vista Plaza
info: Mountain Vista Plaza is a busy shopping center in Surpise, AZ. It has one of the biggest planet fitness in Arizona.

name: Litchfield Marketplace
address: 13830 W Camelback Rd, Litchfield Park, AZ 85340
info: Litchfield Marketplace is a newly built shopping center. It has many restaurants and stores through out the mall.
